    Multi-Purpose Tile Mats

    The multi-purpose tile mats you've always been looking for

    Create a safe and comfortable play area in any location of your home with the lightweight and easy to assemble, non-toxic premium quality high density EVA foam interlocking puzzle piece mats that can be sized to perfection and made into fun shapes for a playful experience. Complete the look of your designated play area with smooth-sided border pieces that come with the mats, providing a neat and safe finish.

    Features & Inspiration

    EFM-24-Multi

    With a thickness of 0.4", these mats protect both your feet and your floors and provide a noise dampening affect that will keep you from annoying your neighbors or family.

    ABC-123

    Don't hesitate to use these alphabet mats in your exercise room so you can exercise while the kids are having fun.

    EFM-25-Multi

    Using border pieces can decrease the risk of tripping over the edges of the mats.

    Ottomanson Inc

    Founded with the aspiration to embellish indoor and outdoor spaces applying a distinct taste and touch while adhering to current trends and worthy customer demands, Ottomanson Inc. gained years of expertise within the home décor industry to best serve this aspiration.

    Read more

    Product description

    The Ottomanson interlocking EVA foam mats, are easy to assemble. In just seconds you can have your very own workout space that feels like the gym. These multipurpose mats reduce fatigue, whether you are working out, using them in the garage or workshop. They can even be used for kids play areas. Perfect for making Hard floor surfaces Soft and comfortable. These soft yet resilient mats can be used for so many purposes. They are also easily cutable to adjust and fit into any space your see fit. Each tile has 2 borders which give you the option to attach as many more tiles for large spaces as needed. Easy to wipe clean, and easy disassembly makes it easy to put away.
